The response is a JSON list with pronunciation analyses of  studentId  '24'.  Note:   The apostrophe in  Bob's  is included in the  graphemes  field of the  s .  When a phoneme represents more than one grapheme like  yo  in  your , they're grouped in the same  graphemes  field.  The  c  in  uncle  exists of two phonemes. The  score  and  verdict  are shown
  per phoneme, along with the  ipa  notation.   HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

